        "en": "1. The General Concepts of Banking <br>2. The Operations of the Bank Tellers<br>3.The Deposits and Remittances in Commerical Banks <br>4. The Commercial Bank Loans(Short-terms Loans and To Investigate and Trace the Loans )<br>5.The Foreign Department <br>6.The Other Businesses of the Bank<br>"
